        <title>C&#43;&#43;：从零开始手搓一个智能指针吧</title>
        <link>https://inariindream.cn/blog/2024/02/27/c-%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%89%8B%E6%90%93%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88%E5%90%A7/</link>
